short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Get a list of screens from your InVision project.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Extension to retrieve the screen name and URL from an InVision project.
It can be used on project and share pages.

Please run it at the following URL.
- https://projects.invisionapp.com/d/main#/projects/prototypes/[ProjectID]
- https://projects.invisionapp.com/share/[ShareID]#/screens?browse
